<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Convita · Tarta Shiitake y Calabaza</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --convita-green: #3A8C3F;
  --convita-dark: #2D6E31;
  --convita-light: #E8F5E9;
  --warm: #F5E6D0;
  --warm-dark: #E8D4B8;
  --earth: #8B6914;
  --shiitake: #6B4226;
  --calabaza: #E87B1F;
  --text: #2C2C2C;
  --text-soft: #5A5A5A;
  --cream: #FFFDF8;
  --sage: #A8C5A0;
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
  font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  color: var(--text);
  background: var(--cream);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ========== HERO ========== */
.hero {
  min-height: 90vh;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-left {
  background: var(--convita-green);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 60px 80px;
  position: relative;
}

.hero-left::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  right: -80px;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 160px;
  background: var(--convita-green);
  clip-path: ellipse(80px 50% at 0% 50%);
}

.brand-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  border-radius: 40px;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  width: fit-content;
  animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
}

.brand-badge svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 68px);
  color: #fff;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  animation: slideUp 0.9s ease-out;
}

.hero-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--warm);
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 440px;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  animation: slideUp 1s ease-out 0.1s both;
}

.hero-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  animation: slideUp 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
}

.hero-tag {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 400;
}

.hero-tag svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; opacity: 0.9; }

.hero-right {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warm) 0%, var(--warm-dark) 100%);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-right::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,123,31,0.15), transparent 70%);
  animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.product-visual {
  width: 380px;
  height: 380px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #D4A25C 0%, #B8862D 40%, #8B6914 100%);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
  box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(107,66,38,0.3), inset 0 -5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  animation: floatIn 1.2s ease-out;
}

.product-visual::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
}

.product-emoji {
  font-size: 120px;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
}

.product-weight {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -20px;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 10px 28px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--text);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.product-weight span { color: var(--convita-green); }

/* ========== COOKING STRIP ========== */
.cooking-strip {
  background: #fff;
  border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  padding: 28px 0;
}

.cooking-inner {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 50px;
  padding: 0 40px;
}

.cook-step {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
}

.cook-icon {
  width: 52px;
  height: 52px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 22px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.cook-icon.preheat { background: #FFF3E0; }
.cook-icon.place { background: #E8F5E9; }
.cook-icon.time { background: #FBE9E7; }

.cook-label { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-soft); line-height: 1.4; }
.cook-label strong { display: block; color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

.cook-arrow {
  color: #ccc;
  font-size: 20px;
}

/* ========== INGREDIENTS SECTION ========== */
.ingredients-section {
  padding: 100px 40px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.section-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 2.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--convita-green);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.section-title {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 48px);
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.section-desc {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--text-soft);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.ingredients-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}

.ingredient-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 32px 24px;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid #f0ede8;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.ingredient-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
}

.ingredient-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.ingredient-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

.ingredient-card.calabaza::before { background: var(--calabaza); }
.ingredient-card.shiitake::before { background: var(--shiitake); }
.ingredient-card.cebolla::before { background: #9C27B0; }
.ingredient-card.garbanzo::before { background: #F9A825; }
.ingredient-card.especias::before { background: var(--convita-green); }

.ing-emoji {
  font-size: 48px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: block;
}

.ing-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  color: var(--text);
}

.ing-benefit {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-soft);
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-weight: 300;
}

/* ========== WELLNESS ICONS SECTION ========== */
.wellness-section {
  background: var(--convita-green);
  padding: 80px 40px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.wellness-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
}

.wellness-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.wellness-section .section-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.wellness-section .section-title { color: #fff; }
.wellness-section .section-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

.wellness-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}

.wellness-badge {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 24px 16px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.wellness-badge:hover {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
}

.wb-icon {
  font-size: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  display: block;
}

.wb-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* ========== OCTOGONOS ========== */
.octogonos-section {
  padding: 70px 40px;
  text-align: center;
  background: var(--convita-light);
}

.octogonos-inner {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.octogonos-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  background: #fff;
  border: 2px solid var(--convita-green);
  border-radius: 60px;
  padding: 16px 36px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.octogonos-badge svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; color: var(--convita-green); }
.octogonos-badge span { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--convita-green); }

.octogonos-text {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--text-soft);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 650px;
  margin: 0 auto 40px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.restrictions-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 30px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.restriction {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.restriction-icon {
  width: 64px;
  height: 64px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #fff;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 28px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  border: 2px solid #e8e8e8;
}

.restriction-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* ========== NUTRITIONAL TABLE ========== */
.nutrition-section {
  padding: 100px 40px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}

.nutrition-left {}

.nutri-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.nutri-table thead {
  background: var(--convita-green);
}

.nutri-table th {
  padding: 14px 20px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: left;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.nutri-table th:last-child { text-align: center; }

.nutri-table td {
  padding: 13px 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
}

.nutri-table td:last-child {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--text-soft);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.nutri-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

.nutri-table tr:hover { background: #fafdf9; }

.nutri-highlight {
  color: var(--convita-green);
  font-weight: 600;
}

.nutri-portion {
  background: var(--convita-light);
  padding: 14px 20px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--convita-dark);
}

.nutri-footnote {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-soft);
  margin-top: 12px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ========== SHIITAKE STORY ========== */
.story-section {
  padding: 100px 40px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cream) 0%, var(--warm) 100%);
}

.story-inner {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.story-question {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px);
  color: var(--shiitake);
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.story-body {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--text-soft);
  line-height: 1.9;
  font-weight: 300;
  text-align: left;
}

.story-body p { margin-bottom: 24px; }

.story-body strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

.story-highlight {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--shiitake), #8B5E3C);
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 36px 40px;
  margin: 40px 0;
  text-align: center;
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ========== CONSERVATION ========== */
.conservation-section {
  padding: 60px 40px;
  background: #fff;
  border-top: 1px solid #eee;
}

.conservation-inner {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}

.cons-card {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 24px 16px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: #fafafa;
  border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
}

.cons-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
.cons-temp { font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.cons-duration { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-soft); font-weight: 300; }

/* ========== FOOTER / CTA ========== */
.cta-section {
  background: var(--convita-green);
  padding: 60px 40px;
  text-align: center;
}

.cta-inner {
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.cta-title {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.cta-text {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.cta-buttons {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border-radius: 40px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
}

.cta-btn.primary {
  background: #fff;
  color: var(--convita-green);
}

.cta-btn.primary:hover { background: var(--warm); transform: translateY(-2px); }

.cta-btn.secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: #fff;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}

.cta-btn.secondary:hover {
  border-color: #fff;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.footer-info {
  margin-top: 40px;
  padding-top: 30px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ========== ANIMATIONS ========== */
@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
@keyframes slideUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
@keyframes floatIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8) translateY(40px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); } }
@keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; } 50% { transform: scale(1.15); opacity: 0.8; } }

/* ========== RESPONSIVE ========== */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
  .hero-left { padding: 60px 30px; }
  .hero-left::after { display: none; }
  .hero-right { padding: 60px 30px; min-height: 400px; }
  .product-visual { width: 280px; height: 280px; }
  .product-emoji { font-size: 80px; }
  .cooking-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
  .cook-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .nutrition-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .conservation-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .ingredients-section, .story-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="brand-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
      Convita · Libre de Gluten
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Tarta <em>Shiitake</em><br>y Calabaza
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      Calabaza asada combinada con hongos shiitake y cebolla, envuelta en una masa crocante. Sin gluten, sin octógonos, sin complicaciones.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-tags">
      <span class="hero-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12l3 3 5-5"/></svg>
        Libre de gluten
      </span>
      <span class="hero-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 3c-4.97 0-9 4.03-9 9s4.03 9 9 9 9-4.03 9-9"/><path d="M15 3a3 3 0 110 6"/></svg>
        Sin lácteos
      </span>
      <span class="hero-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        Sin huevo
      </span>
      <span class="hero-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M7 20l5-5 5 5"/><path d="M12 15V3"/></svg>
        Vegetariano
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="product-visual">
      <span class="product-emoji">🥧</span>
      <div class="product-weight">Peso neto <span>260 g</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== COOKING STRIP ===== -->
<section class="cooking-strip">
  <div class="cooking-inner">
    <div class="cook-step">
      <div class="cook-icon preheat">🔥</div>
      <div class="cook-label"><strong>Precalentar horno</strong>a 180 °C</div>
    </div>
    <span class="cook-arrow">→</span>
    <div class="cook-step">
      <div class="cook-icon place">🧊</div>
      <div class="cook-label"><strong>Colocar congelada</strong>directo al horno</div>
    </div>
    <span class="cook-arrow">→</span>
    <div class="cook-step">
      <div class="cook-icon time">⏱️</div>
      <div class="cook-label"><strong>Hornear 15 min</strong>¡y listo para disfrutar!</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== INGREDIENTS ===== -->
<section class="ingredients-section">
  <div class="section-label">Ingredientes Destacados</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Cada ingrediente, elegido con propósito</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">
    No solo buscamos sabor. Cada componente de esta tarta fue seleccionado por sus propiedades funcionales y su aporte al bienestar.
  </p>
  <div class="ingredients-grid">
    <div class="ingredient-card calabaza">
      <span class="ing-emoji">🎃</span>
      <div class="ing-name">Calabaza</div>
      <div class="ing-benefit">Baja en calorías, rica en fibras, vitaminas A y C, y minerales esenciales. Aporta dulzura natural y cremosidad.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card shiitake">
      <span class="ing-emoji">🍄</span>
      <div class="ing-name">Hongo Shiitake</div>
      <div class="ing-benefit">Alto contenido de proteínas (~18% en seco), fuente de vitamina D y B. Antioxidante, antiinflamatorio y fortalecedor del sistema inmunológico.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card cebolla">
      <span class="ing-emoji">🧅</span>
      <div class="ing-name">Cebolla</div>
      <div class="ing-benefit">Rica en quercetina, vitaminas C y B. Potente prebiótico que favorece la salud intestinal y la microbiota.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ingredient-card garbanzo">
